===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{n-g|Interjection indicating surprise or amazement:}} [[wow]]!, [[gee]]
#: {{zh-x|哇{Wā}！你 的 樣子{zi} 太 酷 了！|Wow! You look terrific!}}
# {{lb|zh|onomatopoeia}} sound of crying
# {{lb|zh|onomatopoeia}} sound of vomiting
# {{lb|zh|classical}} to [[vomit]]
#: {{zh-x|其 兄 自 外 至，曰：『是 鶃鶃 之 肉 也。』出 而 哇{wā} 之。|Just then his brother came into the house, and said, "It is the flesh of that cackling thing," upon which he went out and vomited it.|ref=Mengzi}}
# {{n-g|Sentence-final particle:}} Equivalent of {{zh-l|啊|tr=a}}. Only used after words ending in ''-u, -ao''.
#: {{zh-x|好.哇！|hurray!}}

